<h1>Your Payment Has Been Approved</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @freelancer.name %>,</p>

<p>
  We are pleased to inform you that your payment for the task titled "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>" has been successfully approved.
</p>

<p><strong>Payment Details:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Task:</strong> <%= @task.title %></li>
  <li><strong>Amount:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@payment.amount, unit: "ZMK ") %></li>
  <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= @payment.status.titleize %></li>
</ul>

<p>
  You can now download your completed file by following the link below:
  <%= link_to 'Download Completed File', download_url(@task) %>
</p>

<p>
  Thank you for your excellent work on GigHive! We look forward to more successful collaborations.
</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The GigHive Team</p>
